.name
ColumnSet
.author
Kent Paul Dolan 
.source
Includes source in Modula-2.
.description
A text filter program that takes as input a file with one word per line and
produces a file with these words laid out in the same order in even
columns, as many as will fit across the output screen or page with at least
one space between columns.  
